{"tid":1224030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記住呢陣白色恐怖","createTime":"2019-06-15T01:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T01:54:10.000Z","uid":216008,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3eac3cd328c937425dc35faef89168ccc6e6f0a0","tid":1224030,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:29:56.000Z","msg":"由TG公海拉人，連登仔疑似要被起底，直到琴日執垃圾比人拉真相大白，<br />\n一件又一件事，似乎講比我地聽，束縛自由係咩一回事。<br />\n發夢野完餐，而家就喺旅行途中，其實無乜心情去，但我因為係行動派，而家終於可以以一個旁觀者既角度望成件事。<br />\n第一，班狗而家做既野根本同立左法無分別<br />\n第<br />\n第二，政府放風暫緩，但班狗無停過搞我地<br />\n呢兩樣野，足以睇到所謂暫緩根本又係講一套做一套。<br />\n星期日一返唔到嚟陪大家，但願呢個篇幅細既post，會令大家記住我地仲係要「不散」。<br />\n下星期見"},{"pid":"64cce27a58ec912068dc7a6f01a21d11e3080749","tid":1224030,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:32:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"44f0a699e519ed35097a7f6c6dbc3466c6bee7fe","tid":1224030,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:40:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e739b0842c475025f63fe4f0db1063c028436fd5","tid":1224030,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:41:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"028ad8ec75b90f4cecc83abb13d52afcd56ff375","tid":1224030,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:44:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6017787bbe1b048450d971135aaecc06c36b9cb","tid":1224030,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:45:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f69b7a995bcdff7dc9a13bb0071843308840a2b4","tid":1224030,"uid":259321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:45:37.000Z","msg":"[白色恐怖] 九龍醫院要求上報所有自6月12日的員工請假紀錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1223418</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n白色恐怖唔係第一日<br />\n呢個規模係前所未見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im